data.name: TextBox1.Text
data.value: Nolan was born and raised in Phoenix, Arizona and loved his family very much. He had a very inspirational sister to him, and loved her very much. She helped him become how successful he is today. Nolan has always been intrigued by gaming his whole life, as he started out on the PS3, playing many games since then. His favorite game is Fortnite, and he loves playing with his friends online.

data.name: TextBox2.Text
data.value: Ben was born in Maryland, and moved to Phoenix, Arizona at age 6. Ben grew up playing video games, on PC and many others consoles. Later on, Ben started his business with Nolan, working together to make the best video game store in all of the United States.

data.name: TextBox3.Text
data.value: We created this store in order to spread affordable and quality video games across the country. Pull Games was created because we felt that anyone should be able to experience games, and to make it affordable and possible for all.
